paragraph.example:
[Example: The example below shows several namespace and type declarations along with their associated fully qualified names. 
class A {}        // A  
namespace X       // X  
{  
   class B        // X.B  
   {  
      class C {}   // X.B.C  
   }  
   namespace Y   // X.Y  
   {  
      class D {}   // X.Y.D  
   }  
}  
namespace X.Y    // X.Y  
{  
   class E {}    // X.Y.E  
}  
end example]
